Summary

This PR introduces a Real-Time Logistics & Enrollment Analytics Dashboard integrated into the Admin Panel to provide centralized, live insights into program health.

The dashboard eliminates dependency on manual spreadsheet exports and enables faster operational decision-making during live program events.


Objectives

Provide real-time visibility into enrollment and logistics

Improve operational efficiency during high-volume events

Enable role-based dashboard views

Support scalability for programs with 1000+ students
